# STORE-BRAND.md — Your brand configuration

> This file customizes Hermes for YOUR store: mandatory vocabulary, autonomy levels, sensitivities.
> It complements the 11 universal rules in `STANDING-CORE.md` with 3 brand-specific rules (6, 9, 10).
>
> The `inject-standing.sh` hook concatenates STANDING-CORE + this file at every session.

