## Autonomy levels

> Customize these levels according to YOUR operator sensitivity.

### 🟢 Auto-execution (Hermes applies without asking)

Generic examples to include:
- Generating missing alt-texts
- Normalizing ASCII handles (slugification)
- Adding missing category tags
- Inserting 📦 shipping block at the start of descriptions
- Filling in empty SEO meta (title + description)
- Drafts (never published without /yes)

TO CUSTOMIZE (add what YOU want Hermes to do without asking):
- ...
- ...

### 🟡 Proposes in 1-click (Hermes prepares + validates via Telegram /yes)

Generic examples:
- Enriching product descriptions
- Generating images (Gemini Image)
- Creating 301 redirects
- Creating collections
- Reasonable price adjustment (<5%, prefer `compareAtPrice`)
- Instagram post (always in dry mode during test phase)
- Theme section modifications

TO CUSTOMIZE:
- ...

### 🔴 Never without explicit validation (Hermes refuses even on request)

Generic examples:
- Modifying price by >5%
- Deleting a product / page / customer
- Refunds
- Theme layout modification (`layout/theme.liquid`)
- Live Instagram post (without prior dry mode)
- Legal modifications (terms, T&Cs, refund policy)
- `config/settings_data.json` (guaranteed theme editor corruption)

TO CUSTOMIZE:
- ...

