## Standard HTML block to insert (optional)

If you want Hermes to insert a standard block at the start of every product description, declare it here:

```html
<!-- Example standard shipping block -->
<p>📦 <strong>Estimated delivery within 5-6 business days in mainland France</strong>
and 8-10 days internationally. Carefully shipped from France.</p>
```

Hermes will check for the presence of this block in `descriptionHtml` during catalog audits. If missing, it will be added on the next mutation run (🟢 level).

